<http://www.spektrix.com/yukonartscentre/event/70201ADHVPVLHCVCVCTRPRPPPJCCSKTGL>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Midsummer Opera Gala at the United Church";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Midsummer Opera Gala at the United Church</h1><span><br/></span>Join Edmonton Opera's Emerging Artists and Master Artists for an evening of music, reflection, and community. This special concert will feature a diverse program of sacred music, art song, folk melodies, and select operatic favourites.<span><br/></span>Bringing together artists from across Canada, the concert features Phillip Addis (baritone), Miriam Khalil (soprano), Alex Hetherington (mezzo-soprano), Emerging Artists Teresa Tucci (soprano) and Spencer VanDellen (tenor), with pianist Emily Hamper. Through music that spans traditions, cultures, and generations, the artists invite audiences to gather, listen, and share in an evening of beauty, connection, and song.<span><br/></span>
""";
