  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Scott Ward - Comedy, Hypnosis, and Psychic Trickster Show";
  schema:description """
	Come enjoy a night of amazement and laughter with Hypnotist Scott Ward! A natural with the audience, Scott provides a high quality, hilarious live hypnosis show that will keep you wanting more. Hypnotizing for over two decades, he has entertained thousands of people at events large and small — from the Las Vegas Strip to The Seminole Hard Rock to headlining at the River Cree Casino in Edmonton! Come get hypnotized, mesmerized, and entertained at the Scott Ward Comedy Hypnosis Show, an event suitable for all ages!
""";
